      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk im just really anxious about the flight being so long... it's probably just the stress and the caffeine i had at the airport. if i just try to relax and do those breathing things u mentioned, it'll go away on its own right? i really dont want to go to a hospital in a foreign country if i dont have to.",
